data.description: Charming Country Retreat in Pioneer  Discover the allure of country living in Pioneer, CA, with this delightful two-story home on a spacious 0.33-acre lot. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms across 1,376 sq ft, this residence offers roomy bedrooms and two inviting decks for enjoying the outdoors. A new Generac whole-house generator ensures peace of mind during any power outage. Embrace the tranquility of this quaint country setting and make this charming property your own.Don't miss out on the opportunity for serene, modern country living.  Our location is a gateway to nature's treasures, with parks, hiking trails, and serene lakes nearby. Enjoy the thrill of Kirkwood Ski Resort just an hour away for winter adventures. Experience the allure of South Lake Tahoe in just 1.5 hours,  Sacramento and Stockton 1.5 hr commute. Embrace the best of both worlds with our convenient property location.  All information deemed reliable but should be independently verified.
